########### Run task 1 experiment ###########

Install necessary package in the requirement.txt

1) Download the necessary data

https://github.com/XiaoxiWei/NeurIPS_BEETL/tree/main/start_kits

https://figshare.com/articles/dataset/sleeptutorialdata_zip/14779407

2) generate data format

go to EEG_Lightning/NeurIPS_1 to run python generate_task_1_final_data.py

You need to define
source_path = "C:/Users/wduong/mne_data/SleepSource/SleepSource"
final_target_sleep_data = "C:\\Users\\wduong\\mne_data\\finalSleep\\sleep_target\\"
final_test_sleep_data = "C:\\Users\\wduong\\mne_data\\finalSleep\\testing\\"

source_path is where you store the source sleep data
final_target_sleep_data and final_test_sleep_data are where you store the sleep target data and test data

The matlab data is generated in the directory EEG_Lightning/da_dataset/NeurIPS_1/

3) The experiment is located in NeurIPS_1/task_1_final_1

4) run the training script

Go to train_script/gpu_4_script/experiment_script_4.0.sh to define the location of the train script and data path

computer_dir="/home/wduong/tmp/EEG_Lightning"
data_path_dir="/data1/wduong_experiment_data/EEG_Lightning/"

computer_dir is where you store the EEG_Lightning
data_path_dir is where you store the data. We recommend that you store the data in da_dataset folder in EEG_Lightning/da_dataset

Define the conda enviroment in train_script/gpu_4_script/experiment_script_4.0.sh
conda activate #your conda enviroment

run bash experiment_script_4.0.sh to train the model automatically


5) Generate predict file

Go to EEG_Lightning/tools/process_predict_task_1.py

result_path = "C:\\wduong_folder\Dassl.pytorch-master\\NeurIPS_competition\\EEG_Dassl_Lightning\\NeurIPS_1\\task_1_final_1\\quick_ver_1_1\\tune_cla\\no_aug\\no_norm\\deepsleep_vanilla\\full_dataset\\model\\predict_folder"

case="task_1"

Define the result_path where you store the data in result_path

The .txt file with the test data prediction is generated in the folder EEG_Lightning/tools/util/task_1/


########### Run task 2 experiment ###########

1) Download the necessary data

https://github.com/XiaoxiWei/NeurIPS_BEETL/tree/main/start_kits

https://github.com/XiaoxiWei/NeurIPS_BEETL/blob/main/start_kits/3.motor_imagery_kit.ipynb

2) generate data format

go to EEG_Lightning/NeurIPS_2 to run python generate_task_2_final_data.py

You need to define
data_path = "C:\\Users\\wduong\\mne_data\\finalMI"

To get source dasets, we use moabb

data_path are where you store the target and test MI data

The matlab data is generated in the directory EEG_Lightning/da_dataset/NeurIPS_2/

3) The experiment is located in NeurIPS_2/task_2_final_2

4) run the training script

Go to train_script/gpu_2_script/experiment_script_2.0.sh to define the location of the train script and data path

computer_dir="/home/wduong/tmp/EEG_Lightning"
data_path_dir="/data1/wduong_experiment_data/EEG_Lightning/"

computer_dir is where you store the EEG_Lightning
data_path_dir is where you store the data. We recommend that you store the data in da_dataset folder in EEG_Lightning/da_dataset

Define the conda enviroment in train_script/gpu_2_script/experiment_script_2.0.sh
conda activate #your conda enviroment

run bash experiment_script_2.0.sh to train the model automatically


5) Generate predict file

Go to EEG_Lightning/tools/process_predict_task_2.py

result_path = "C:\\wduong_folder\Dassl.pytorch-master\\NeurIPS_competition\\EEG_Dassl_Lightning\\NeurIPS_1\\task_1_final_1\\quick_ver_1_1\\tune_cla\\no_aug\\no_norm\\deepsleep_vanilla\\full_dataset\\model\\predict_folder"

case="task_1"

Define the result_path where you store the data in result_path

The .txt file with the test data prediction is generated in the folder EEG_Lightning/tools/util/task_1/




